						<ul class="quotations-list">
							
							<li class="posRe">
								<blockquote style="width: 500px;">
									''Poetry is the supreme fiction, madame.
<br />Take the moral law and make a nave of it
<br />And from the nave build haunted heaven.''
								</blockquote>
								<cite>
	                                Wallace Stevens (1879-1955), U.S. poet. A High-Toned Old Christian Woman, Harmonium (1923).
								</cite>
								
								<div class="Quo03">
				                    
	
	
