							</li>
							
							<li class="posRe">
								<blockquote style="width: 500px;">
									That other one wanted to think his way to life,
<br />Sure that the ultimate poem was the mind,
<br />Or of the mind, or of the mind in these
<br />Elysia, these days, half earth, half mind;
<br /...
								</blockquote>
								<cite>
	                                Wallace Stevens (1879-1955), U.S. poet. "Extracts from Addresses to the Academy of Fine Ideas."
								</cite>
								
