							<li class="posRe">
								<blockquote style="width: 500px;">
									How clean the sun when seen in its idea,
<br />Washed in the remotest cleanliness of a heaven
<br />That has expelled us and our images . . .
<br />The death of one god is the death of all.
<br />...
								</blockquote>
								<cite>
	                                Wallace Stevens (1879-1955), U.S. poet. "Notes toward a Supreme Fiction."
								</cite>
								
