							<li class="posRe">
								<blockquote style="width: 500px;">
									''The sorry verities!
<br />Yet in excess, continual,
<br />There is cure of sorrow.''
								</blockquote>
								<cite>
	                                Wallace Stevens (1879-1955), U.S. poet. "The Weeping Burgher."
								</cite>
								
								<div class="Quo03">
				                    
	
	
